  33 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsMustHave","name":"alcarecategorize","version":"1.0.5","tab":"quick_bulk_update","displayName":"Copy & Move Products Between Categories - Dropshipping","description":"With this module, you move or copy products massively between categories. Especially useful for DROPSHIPPING and to synchronize products with your ERP","description_full":"With this module, you move or copy products massively between categories. Especially useful for DROPSHIPPING and to synchronize products with your ERP. It allows cleaning categories and moving both entire categories and specific products.","author":"Alcalink","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"Streamline the movement of your products, you will have the store fully organized quickly, easily and efficiently. The most useful module for Dropshipping and for synchronization with an ERP, since you can move \\/ copy products by hand, but also by means of a PROGRAMMED TASK.\\u00a0MOVE \\/ COPY \\/ CLEAN COMPLETE CATEGORIES\\u00a0You can move complete categories only by choosing the source category and the destination category. In this way, the products will no longer appear in the source category, to appear in the destination category.\\u00a0You also have the option to copy one category into another. The products of the source category will also appear in the destination category, so your products will have more visibility and increase the sales of your store.\\u00a0If necessary, you can also clean an entire category, so the products in that category will belong to the start category of your Prestashop.\\u00a0MOVE \\/ COPY SPECIFIC PRODUCTS\\u00a0If you are interested in not moving the entire category, if you only want to move certain products you can also do it very easily. You can search through a filter the category you want and select the products you want to move or copy. In the same way, if you move them they will appear in the destination category, while if the copies will appear in the destination category, as well as in the origin.\\u00a0SEARCH FILTER\\u00a0To facilitate the selection of categories, a filter with text has been enabled to avoid wasting time in tedious infinite deployments. You can search for the desired category and select it instantly.\\u00a0SCHEDULED TASK\\u00a0If you do not have much time to make the changes there is no problem, for this we have the option to do it through a scheduled task that you will add in your Hosting and that will make the changes you want automatically.\\u00a0An organized store will automatically transform into an increase in sales.\\u00a0Available in several different languages, such as Spanish, English, Italian or French.\\u00a0In a few minutes you will have learned to make use of our module, since you have at your disposal a documentation explaining step by step installation, configuration and operation.","compatibility":{"from":"1.6.0.4","to":"1.7.8.8"},"nb_rates":null,"avg_rate":null,"badges":{"badge":"https:\\/\\/medias2.prestastore.com\\/themes\\/prestastore\\/img\\/front\\/sprites\\/badges\\/module-editor.png"},"url":{"0":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/mass-updates\\/28959-copy-move-products-between-categories-dropshipping.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download"},"image":"..\\/img\\/tmp\\/7879f267f9b0d3daa3e0631d6bbf35b1.jpg","addons_buy_url":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/mass-updates\\/28959-copy-move-products-between-categories-dropshipping.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download","installed":false,"database_version":0,"interest":0}',
