  57 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsMustHave","name":"feedmanager","version":"1.7.3","tab":"advertising_marketing","displayName":"Feed Manager Pro (Product feeds for all platforms)","description":"All feeds in one module. Create your own feeds or get more feeds by request for free. Google Merchant Center, Adwords, Facebook feeds are included out of box with easy and feature rich settings","description_full":"All feeds in one module. Create your own feeds or get more feeds by request for free. Google Merchant Center, Adwords, Facebook feeds are included out of box with easy and feature rich settings.","author":"Community developer","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"This module adds Google\\/Bing Merchant Center, Google Adwords Business Data, Facebook product feeds and any other feed via customizable feed&nbsp;templates. It also provides the product feed for dynamic remarketing via Analytics, which is the only way to have dynamic remarketing in countries, that are not supported by the Google Merchant Center. Main features:Customizable universal feeds (create your own feeds or download them for free)Google\\/Bing Merchant Center product feed (works also on many other platforms)Google Adwords Business Data product feed \\u2013 remarketing via analyticsFacebook product catalog feedSupports custom feed export of products, manufacturers, categories, currencies and carriersProducts can be filtered by tags, product range, price, manufacturer, supplier, category, attributes, features and product IDsGZIP compressionsupports very large shops (can also split products into multiple feeds)Automatic feed updates (via simple URL access or cron tasks)Supports additional images Custom feed templates for download (more can be added by request for free):https:\\/\\/prestashop.infinia.systems\\/templates\\/ Custom Feeds (if your feed is not on the list just ask):CeneoGlamiIdealoKelkooStileoYandexHeurekaZboziFacebook country\\/language Facebook\\/Google Video Tutorial:https:\\/\\/www.youtube.com\\/embed\\/CYNpds_pxQA Facebook example:https:\\/\\/prestashop.infinia.systems\\/feed_manager\\/modules\\/feedmanager\\/feed_facebook\\/feed.php Merchant Center example:https:\\/\\/prestashop.infinia.systems\\/feed_manager\\/modules\\/feedmanager\\/feed_merchant\\/feed.php Adwords example:https:\\/\\/prestashop.infinia.systems\\/feed_manager\\/modules\\/feedmanager\\/feed_adwords\\/feed.php","compatibility":{"from":"1.5.0.0","to":"8.0.1"},"nb_rates":null,"avg_rate":null,"badges":null,"url":{"0":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/sea-paid-search-engine-advertising\\/32728-feed-manager-pro-product-feeds-for-all-platforms.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download"},"image":"..\\/img\\/tmp\\/4781c27d806fe92acfcd1c5236bc36fa.jpg","addons_buy_url":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/sea-paid-search-engine-advertising\\/32728-feed-manager-pro-product-feeds-for-all-platforms.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download","installed":false,"database_version":0,"interest":0}',
  58 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsMustHave","name":"freedeliverymanager","version":"1.6.21","tab":"shipping_logistics","displayName":"Free Delivery Manager","description":"This is the ideal solution to increase the amount of the average sales transaction","description_full":"This is the ideal solution to increase the amount of the average sales transaction. According to the rules you have chosen, you encourage customers to increase the value of their purchases in order to take advantage of free delivery.","author":"TimActive","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"Developing your sales by increasing the value of transactions has never been an easy thing to implement. The &ldquo;Free Delivery Manager&rdquo; module is actually the perfect solution for offering your respected customers free shipping through objective rules. It is the promise of a rise in the amount of orders with total control of delivery costs.  The module allows you to calculate in advance, with the help of precise rules, the necessary conditions for unlocking free delivery. The management and monitoring are done according to carriers, delivery area, price, weight, or any other criteria you term as important for your business.  The &ldquo;Free Delivery Manager&rdquo; module offers control of delivery costs by releasing delivery available as a function of criteria you have chosen. All the carriers have their own price list. You may, for example, indicate a minimum order amount by carrier In presenting to the customer, in their order summary, the amount remaining before delivery is available, so you definitely encourage them to order more.  Highly detailed statistics visually present two types of reports together. The first one presents the number of orders that have benefited from free delivery, as well as the total and per-order amount that this cost you. You really control the impact of delivery costs. The second report displays the detail of costs caused by free postage and the orders where the rules for free shipping are applied. Thus, the &ldquo;Free Delivery Manager&rdquo; module increases the value of transactions as well as the number of orders!  This module has been constantly evolving, many thanks to user feedback. TimActive, in fact, grants great importance to your perception of our solutions and of the improvements that can be added.&nbsp;","compatibility":{"from":"1.5.0.0","to":"1.7.8.8"},"nb_rates":null,"avg_rate":null,"badges":{"badge":["https:\\/\\/medias2.prestastore.com\\/themes\\/prestastore\\/img\\/front\\/sprites\\/badges\\/ps-selected.png","https:\\/\\/medias2.prestastore.com\\/themes\\/prestastore\\/img\\/front\\/sprites\\/badges\\/module-editor.png"]},"url":{"0":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/shipping-costs\\/8895-free-delivery-manager.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download"},"image":"..\\/img\\/tmp\\/ccb6d4a6506f913766693f1ad830b72f.jpg","addons_buy_url":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/shipping-costs\\/8895-free-delivery-manager.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download","installed":false,"database_version":0,"interest":0}',
  59 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsNative","name":"usercentrics","version":"1.0.13","tab":"administration","displayName":"GDPR Cookie Banner by Usercentrics","description":"Comprehensive and easy to configure, this module enables your store to become compliant with the latest data privacy regulations applicable to your country and to assure your customers that you are se","description_full":"Comprehensive and easy to configure, this module enables your store to become compliant with the latest data privacy regulations applicable to your country and to assure your customers that you are securely storing and managing their data.&nbsp;","author":"Silbersaiten","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"This module will help you inform your online store visitors about the cookies and trackers installed on your website. You can easily collect, manage and store their consent while also achieving GDPR cookie compliance.&nbsp;Usercentrics GDPR cookie banner provides:&nbsp;a fast and easy way to help you achieve GDPR compliancea user-friendly and fully automated process to collect, manage and document your website visitors&rsquo; consentprotection from data privacy violations for your store","compatibility":{"from":"1.6.0.4","to":"1.7.8.8"},"nb_rates":null,"avg_rate":null,"badges":{"badge":"https:\\/\\/medias2.prestastore.com\\/themes\\/prestastore\\/img\\/front\\/sprites\\/badges\\/ps-official-partner.png"},"url":{"0":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/legal\\/50763-gdpr-cookie-banner-by-usercentrics.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download"},"image":"..\\/img\\/tmp\\/29c113cb0661c7b5f668cceaa1d7602d.jpg","installed":false,"database_version":0,"interest":0}',
  60 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsMustHave","name":"deluxecookies","version":"4.8.2","tab":"administration","displayName":"GDPR Cookies Law (Advice - Audit - Blocking)","description":"Complies with the European Cookies Law (included in GDPR). Displays an advice with information about the Cookies used in your shop and allows the customer to block cookies that do not interest them","description_full":"Complies with the European Cookies Law (included in GDPR). Displays an advice with information about the Cookies used in your shop and allows the customer to block cookies that do not interest them. Includes powerful store cookie auditing system.","author":"InnovaDeluxe","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"We will help your customers to accept cookies policy of your store to obey with the law on data collection. This module runs in your online store when your cookies legal texts, are clearly specifying what type of cookies are you using and what is the data collecting destination.To determine the type of cookies you are using, please ask an expert to check your Prestashop store. To learn how to prepare the legal text you need to include in your store, you can ask a GDPR and LSSI experienced adviser or check this guide provided by the Official Data Protection Agency. The module includes a powerful auditing system, to check which cookies are generating internally the modules you have installed. The module will review each section of the front office of your store and will list all the cookies detected, which you can categorize to show the information of each one in the cookie advice. At this time, you cannot audit cookies from external domains, but you can add them manually. You can use any extension for your browser and then add them manually to the module. A new and much more powerful cookie warning has been 