  108 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsMustHave","name":"totshowmailalerts","version":"2.0.1","tab":"administration","displayName":"Product Out of Stock : Emails and Number of Requests","description":"Discover the #1 solution that allows you to learn which out-of-stock products are your clients most interested in. Show custom button in FrontOffice. Export email addresses in .csv","description_full":"Discover the #1 solution that allows you to learn which out-of-stock products are your clients most interested in. Show custom button in FrontOffice. Export email addresses in .csv. Notify your client of the sales end.","author":"202 ecommerce","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"Obtain an practical glance at your client\\u2019s most desired out-of-stock products. This module, which is complementary of the free module \\u201cEmail Alerts\\u201d allows you to retrieve the numbers and email adresses of the clients that demand a notification in case of product restocking. Therefore, a specific field\\u00a0 will be displayed in the product sheet for the clients to prompt their email addresses in case of restocking.New ! Customize the button styles and show it on the product page.\\u00a0Optimize your supplier and restocking orders thanks to the ability to see the out-of-stock products interest your clients the most.\\u00a0Improve your customer experience and monitoring by customizing your steps according to theirs and making the best out of the \\u201cMail Alerts\\u201d module. For instance, you could block the automatic email delivery and put in place an email which recommends similar products, to the one that is out-of-stock, with the implementation and delivery of a personalized newsletter for your clients. You can thus take actions to refocus your client\\u2019s purchase intentions.\\u00a0Export data stored in CSV format and integrate them to your newsletter or to a customer management software. Using this module you can see and export the list of product that your customers wish to buy.\\u00a0Perfect integration with the \\u201cMail Alers\\u201d native Prestashop module that notifies your customers of the availability of the stock producs that they wanted to follow.\\u00a0Delete the alerts if you want not to notify your customers about product availability.\\u00a0In addition to the enhanced monitoring of the your wanted out-of-stock products, and the optimized stocking that this brings, this module also allows you to take actions to improve the purchase experience of your customers.\\u00a0","compatibility":{"from":"1.6.1.0","to":"1.7.8.7"},"nb_rates":null,"avg_rate":null,"badges":{"badge":"https:\\/\\/medias2.prestastore.com\\/themes\\/prestastore\\/img\\/front\\/sprites\\/badges\\/module-editor.png"},"url":{"0":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/stock-supplier-management\\/6320-product-out-of-stock-emails-and-number-of-requests.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download"},"image":"..\\/img\\/tmp\\/d5821472e2113d73ceb20a213aaaf1c4.jpg","addons_buy_url":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/stock-supplier-management\\/6320-product-out-of-stock-emails-and-number-of-requests.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download","installed":false,"database_version":0,"interest":0}',
  109 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsMustHave","name":"amppages","version":"1.0.8","tab":"administration","displayName":"PROFESSIONAL AMP PAGES - ACCELERATED MOBILE PAGES","description":"The First AMP module built for PrestaShop is finally on Add-ons. Over 80 prebuilt features. 100% Template Independent - will work with any template used","description_full":"The First AMP module built for PrestaShop is finally on Add-ons. Over 80 prebuilt features. 100% Template Independent - will work with any template used. 7X times faster Mobile Page based on Google\'s AMP project.","author":"PRESTACHAMPS","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"\\u00a0ChangelogIf the AMP module works properly on your site, please do not update the module!\\u00a0- Bug fixing regarding the images load on the category page\\u00a0- We have implemented the possibility to add a link to the slider on the AMP pages.- Fixed the out of stock problem on the category pages.- The Custom text field on the home page is multilanguage ready from now.\\u00a0Benefits for Merchants\\u00a0You\'ve always been wondering how to create efficient and straightforward mobile page. If you\'re checking this module, it means that you already know that more than 60% of your customers are coming from a Mobile device, the problem is always how to turn them to buyers or customers. Speed and functionality (simplicity is the key), have always been the two major factors when it comes to sales.\\u00a0We tend to overcomplicate things, and we forget that people checking stuff on mobile are time-dependent, they need the essentials,\\u00a0and motivation to make the purchase.\\u00a0What will this module offer you: \\u00a01. Seven times faster mobile page - no more VPS or Dedicated server is needed to have a quick Mobile version. Google caches the mobile result, and it\'s served to your customer at a ridiculous speed - It\'s almost Instant2.Boost your mobile results into the TOP placements in Google Mobile Search.3. Significantly higher conversion rate.4. We know that templates are always an issue, so we created one for you for free.5. We created 3 category and product page types, which allows you to conduct A\\/B tests based on Google Optimize.6. We have the most fantastic support out there, and we continuously develop our module. Our Goal is to offer you the most comprehensive AMP theme and Module out there.7.\\u00a0 Google Already announced that he\'s testing the AMP version on Tablets. Stay tuned to the new demands.8. Over 500 stores are using this module already\\u00a0","compatibility":{"from":"1.6.0.4","to":"1.6.1.24"},"nb_rates":null,"avg_rate":null,"badges":{"badge":"https:\\/\\/medias2.prestastore.com\\/themes\\/prestastore\\/img\\/front\\/sprites\\/badges\\/module-editor.png"},"url":{"0":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/website-performances\\/26950-professional-amp-pages-accelerated-mobile-pages.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download"},"image":"..\\/img\\/tmp\\/a4d12d0f9e58c07641d980ada3b88ea6.jpg","addons_buy_url":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/website-performances\\/26950-professional-amp-pages-accelerated-mobile-pages.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download","installed":false,"database_version":0,"interest":0}',
  110 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsMustHave","name":"proaccount","version":"1.3.2","tab":"administration","displayName":"Professionnal account (B2B)","description":"Business Account provides a dedicated page for the registration of professionals. Additional required fields for the user and a specific email at registration is sent to the merchant","description_full":"Business Account provides a dedicated page for the registration of professionals. Additional required fields for the user and a specific email at registration is sent to the merchant. Assigns automaticaly a customer in a specific group.&nbsp;","author":"DM Concept","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"The Business To Business (B2B) market is essential, it is necessary to offer an offer dedicated to the specific needs of your business customers.&nbsp;The B2B Business Account module allows you to set up the creation of specific business accounts with broader possibilities than a basic account. It allows to have a space dedicated to professionals, adapting to their needs.&nbsp;The Business Account defines a CMS page that contains information related to the interest and benefits of creating a business account. The administration of this CMS page allows you to detail the information prior to a registration of your customers for the B2B market.&nbsp;By configuring these accounts for the B2B market, you have the ability to manage the display of form fields to suit your business customers.&nbsp;By building your registration form for the business accounts, you can define the optional and mandatory fields. This customization allows you to adapt the Prestashop B2B mode to your industry.&nbsp;You adapt to the needs of your B2B market by allowing your customers to create a professional account. To register, they must complete certain information specific t