  133 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsMustHave","name":"zipcodezone","version":"2.0.3","tab":"shipping_logistics","displayName":"Shipping fees based on postal codes","description":"Apply different shipping fees based on postal codes of your customers","description_full":"Apply different shipping fees based on postal codes of your customers.","author":"Community developer","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"Do you want to have more control over your shipping costs? This module is made for you. In just a few clicks, you will have suitable carriers and precise shipping costs according to your client&#39;s postal code!&nbsp;Divide your countries into as many delivery zones as you want. Regions, departments, islands, ect ... you have control over the division to ensure that you have the most accurate shipping costs, by price or weight ranges. You can also choose not to deliver an area.&nbsp;All postal codes around the world are compatible, whether you deliver to a country with numeric postal codes, or alphanumeric such as Canada.&nbsp;The module also has a CSV import. If you have a large number of postal codes, you can prepare your rules in your usual spreadsheet and then import them into the module. You will also have the possibility of exporting your configuration in CSV, to make a backup or to carry out several modifications quickly.&nbsp;You will also benefit from less fraud. No more customers who live in remote areas and who take advantage of this to order with reduced shipping costs. They will either have adjusted shipping costs, or the delivery will be blocked depending on your choice.","compatibility":{"from":"1.6.0.4","to":"8.0.1"},"nb_rates":null,"avg_rate":null,"badges":null,"url":{"0":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/shipping-costs\\/5711-shipping-fees-based-on-postal-codes.html?utm_source=