  141 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsMustHave","name":"facebookpsconnect","version":"4.0.3","tab":"social_networks","displayName":"Social Login: Facebook Google TikTok Amazon Twitter\\u2026","description":"Offer your visitors a social connect function to create their account or login in 1 click with Facebook, Google, TikTok, PayPal, Amazon, Twitter or LinkedIn","description_full":"Offer your visitors a social connect function to create their account or login in 1 click with Facebook, Google, TikTok, PayPal, Amazon, Twitter or LinkedIn. Social Login installs the buttons to connect with social networks.","author":"Business Tech","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"New!\\u00a0Offer now instant connection via TikTok, the social network with a billion active users! Did you know that one of the main purchase obstacles on the Internet is to have to create a custom account?\\u00a0With \\"Social Login\\" module, boost your conversion rate by letting your customers easily register and log in to your shop through their favorite social network: Facebook, Google, TikTok, Twitter, Amazon, PayPal, or even LinkedIn! REDUCE YOUR ABANDONED CART RATE ! This is a known fact in the world of e-commerce that\\u00a0the less friction there is during checkout, the higher the chance is that the customer will finalize his or her order.\\u00a0By removing the account creation step, you significantly reduce the shopping cart abandonment rate on your shop. How to do it? By using the connection of Internet users\\u00a0to the social networks. Indeed, the use of social networks is growing at an unprecedented rate, especially since the beginning of the Covid-19 crisis. There are now\\u00a0more than 4 billion active users\\u00a0in the world.So do not hesitate any more and use this incredible craze to your advantage!\\u00a0Allow your visitors to create a customer account\\u00a0instantly\\u00a0on your store, using their favorite social network, to which they are permanently connected. No more account creation or identification forms, which are real obstacles to conversion. Thanks to our \\"Social Login\\" module, Internet users, whether they already have an account on your shop or not, connect\\u00a0in only one click\\u00a0via\\u00a0Facebook, Google, TikTok, Twitter, Amazon, PayPal or even LinkedIn.No need to remember their password anymore! Even when changing device: whether they are on their smartphone or their tablet, a simple click on the social login button is enough to connect to their account on your store. Moreover, if they use a PayPal connection, their shipping\\/billing address is also automatically filled in their account. But that\'s not all! You can go even further in\\u00a0simplifying the shopping tunnel\\u00a0by linking \\"Social Login\\" with Presta-Module\'s\\u00a0\\"One Click Order\\"\\u00a0module and offering your customers, not only the\\u00a0one-click connection, but also\\u00a0the one-click order!\\u00a0Placing an order on your site has never been so easy!Find out\\u00a0\\"One Click Order\\"\\u00a0here:\\u00a0https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/en\\/payment-card-wallet\\/29273-one-click-order-buy-in-one-click.html TOTAL FREEDOM IN POSITIONING YOUR CONNECTORS The module offers you\\u00a0multiple possibilities to position\\u00a0your connectors and even goes so far as to leave you the hand to precisely place your connection buttons.In fact, in addition to the standard positions such as, among others, the login page or the order tunnel, the module provides you with\\u00a0an advanced positioning tool for your connectors:\\u00a0simply select the HTML element on which you want to see the buttons, fill it in the configuration and the module takes care of everything! A NEAT DESIGN AND ADVANCED CUSTOMIZATION OF THE CONNECTION BLOCKS Our \\"Social Login\\" module,\\u00a0totally responsive,\\u00a0has been implemented\\u00a0according to the latest standards\\u00a0provided by social networks. The ergonomics of the buttons has been worked on to allow the best user experience, whatever the type of device used (smartphone, tablet, desktop computer, ...). In addition, regardless of the position chosen for your login buttons, the module provides you with\\u00a0a complete CSS tool\\u00a0allowing you to\\u00a0fully customize\\u00a0the appearance of each connection block, in a completely\\u00a0independent way.\\u00a0 Finally, in order to best adapt to the design of your site, the module also allows you to choose, for each position of the connectors, between\\u00a0standard or mini size buttons. Also, you can add a shaded effect under the buttons and\\u00a0round the edges\\u00a0for a perfect finish!   Take advantage of this\\u00a0customization flexibility\\u00a0to make your shop visually unique! A CONFIGURATION ADAPTED TO ALL The module is suitable for all skill levels! Benefit from a\\u00a0clear, intuitive and documented\\u00a0configuration interface that allows you to set up your login buttons as quickly and efficiently as possible. Choose the default positions defined by the module for an ultra-fast installation. You have some technical skills? Use the advanced positioning tool of the module! ","compatibility":{"from":"1.6.1.0","to":"1.7.8.5"},"nb_rates":null,"avg_rate":null,"badges":{"badge":"https:\\/\\/medias2.prestastore.com\\/themes\\/prestastore\\/img\\/front\\/sprites\\/badges\\/module-editor.png"},"url":{"0":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/social-login-connect\\/8204-social-login-facebook-google-tiktok-amazon-twitter.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download"},"image":"..\\/img\\/tmp\\/dcc8def6fc98e9ad854f7bbe205f7960.jpg","addons_buy_url":"https:\\/\\/addons.prestashop.com\\/ru\\/social-login-connect\\/8204-social-login-facebook-google-tiktok-amazon-twitter.html?utm_source=back-office&utm_medium=push-addons&utm_campaign=back-office-RU&utm_content=download","installed":false,"database_version":0,"interest":0}',
  142 => '{"id":0,"warning":"","type":"addonsNative","name":"springxbs","version":"1.4.4","tab":"shipping_logistics","displayName":"SPRING GDS - Worldwide delivery solutions","description":"Access over 230 worldwide carriers today! Spring GDS offers you fast and easy set up of delivery options. Our team of experts is here to help your international business grow further","description_full":"Access over 230 worldwide carriers today! Spring GDS offers you fast and easy set up of delivery options. Our team of experts is here to help your international business grow further.","author":"PrestaShop Partners","limited_countries":[],"parent_class":"","onclick_option":false,"is_configurable":0,"need_instance":0,"not_on_disk":1,"available_on_addons":1,"trusted":1,"active":0,"additional_description":"Spring GDS module makes international shipping easier for medium and large e-shops with expanding cross-border business.&nbsp;With more than 230 logistical carriers, we provide worldwide shipping solutions for your parcels up to 20 kg. The module enables you to:&nbsp;Create and print your own shipping labels directly from your orders&nbsp;Select shipping service of your choice (untracked, tracked, or with signature)&nbsp;Track your parcels for a better follow-up&nbsp;Choose the best local carriers for your customers abroad&nbsp;Benefit from good transit times and attractive rates for these key destinations:o&nbsp;&nbsp; Within Europe (3-5 days): France, Spain, Italy, Germany, Benelux, UKo&nbsp;&nbsp; Europe to Asia (7 days): China, Japan, South Koreao&nbsp;&nbsp; Europe to America (7-10 days): Canada, USA&nbsp;Get access to all this within your back-office and PrestaShop environment. &nbsp;&nbsp;You will also like:&nbsp;Tailored Brexit solutions and a landed costs calculator to continue to ship easily to UK&nbsp;Proactive and multilingual advisors dedicated especially to your shipments and your international growth","compatibility":{"from":"1.5.1.0","to":"1.7.5.0"},"nb_rates":null